works.description:
The owner of the site below clearly stole my material, if you compare their page  with my authorized page.  I am a doctor who happens to treat these types of conditions on a daily basis, while the owner of the unauthorized site does not even identify who they are.  In my opinion, they just put up the site to try and rank for long tail keyword "top of foot pain".
Normally a site of this poor quality should be buried on page 155 or worse in Google rankings but they are number 1.  How come Panda and Penguin did not weed  them out?
